query:
SELECT 
  ii.id as item_id,
  e.name as environment_name,
  ist.id as step_id,
  ist.step_order,
  ist.step_name,
  ist.completed_quantity
FROM inspection_items ii
LEFT JOIN environments e ON ii.environment_id = e.id
LEFT JOIN installation_steps ist ON ii.id = ist.inspection_item_id
ORDER BY e.name, ist.step_order;
